Play Widevine-protected video in Chromium.
This adds the ChromeOS DRM video decoding library to Chromium, and a ChromeOS user-agent. Websites you browse will think your Pi is a Chromebook!
To run: Menu -> Internet -> Chromium Media Edition.
To test DRM: https://bitmovin.com/demos/drm
For non-DRM websites, you should use the original Chromium launcher.
This works on these websites:
• Netflix
• Hulu
• Amazon Prime
• Disney+
• HBO
• Spotify
• Pandora
• Hoopla
• MUBI
• BritBox
• Bell Satellite TV
